/obj/item/paper{
	info = "The Horizon is apparently stationed over Volturno of all places while in-system, which is just our luck. We've got a good number of our standard menu items in the freezers in the back that we can quickly reheat and serve if we get mobbed, just don't make it obvious if you're not making it fresh.<br><br>Remember, this month we've got the gyros, fries, doner kebabs, falafel, tossed salad, and chocolate pitas.<br><br>Don't take any shit from these people, and call me if there's trouble.<br><br><i>-Donny</i>";
